im (1\\%,4\\%)$,\nwhich can be more than two order smaller if considering the 3G detector\nnetwork.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 Mar 2020 09:34:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Aug 2020 01:15:23 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 24 Aug 2020 07:37:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-07"}
