ets and is able to capture the nonstationary diurnal and\nseasonal variations of the wind speed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Mar 2020 17:25:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Feb 2021 21:22:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-02"}
